  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0d9a \u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dc4\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0da0\u0ddd\u0daf\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An accusation from Nalaka Godaheva to the government",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliament member Dr. Nalaka Godaheva says that the government does not have a plan and does not give space to those who talk about a plan.",
        "The MP states that he did not see any plan in Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe's speech in Parliament yesterday (5), and that the International Monetary Fund is currently backing away from assistance because the government does not have a proper plan.",
        "In a note on his official Facebook account, the member stated that he was ready to comment on the current economic crisis in the parliament today (6) morning, and he was informed by the office of the chief organizer of the ruling party that he would be given 3 minutes. have",
        "He has also stated that he is questioning what is the plan for building the country presented by those who get hours to speak in the parliament."
      ],
